{"tid":1929624,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【本土文化】黃色音樂需要行動支持!此帖將不定期分享好歌&好音樂人!","createTime":"2020-03-17T05:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T06:13:12.000Z","uid":121855,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8624a1c48fa0d2019dd1c591296d50af03d3eb7c","tid":1929624,"uid":121855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T05:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zvwogqv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzvwogqv.jpg&h=5ad52452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oGZk25x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoGZk25x.jpg&h=9da5e658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZEwvFSf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZEwvFSf.jpg&h=889ad4c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acd5e40397040e897b1dcd312efd81572363bc50","tid":1929624,"uid":121855,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T05:14:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YyD3TluW6MY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYyD3TluW6MY&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8PYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=67345d69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YyD3TluW6MY</a><br />\n//對上一隻碟係2017年年尾，呢兩年香港人經歷咗太多太多，<br />\n喺呢兩年做呢隻碟都真係要面對唔少人生課題...<br />\n呢隻碟裡面最後一首歌《黑鏡》係盧凱彤作曲。<br />\n原本呢首係碟裡面第一首派台歌，<br />\n那時候正正就是Ellen離開的時候，<br />\n而呢首歌咁啱又係講關於生死，<br />\n呢個課題當時對我黎講真係好大好大。<br />\n到今日《黑鏡》變成碟裡面最後一首歌，<br />\n呢兩年嘅事情彷彿冥冥中有曬安排，<br />\n到咗合適嘅時候自然就成形，不能計劃亦不能強求。<br />\n生命這趟旅程也不是只有自己，<br />\n我們是一個共同體，無論好與壞我地大家都一齊Ride Along緊，<br />\n人在世轉個圈，人生好短，<br />\n能夠同時喺呢個空間呢個維度一齊出現真係要好有緣份先得。<br />\n人慢慢長大先知我地經歷嘅一切一切真係好X難得🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n《Before I forget》<br />\n呢隻碟係呢兩年我同我身邊好重要嘅人，<br />\n用大家寶貴嘅生命，時間，心血，一齊共同創造出黎。<br />\n每首歌背後記載著呢兩年好多獨一無二嘅Moments，<br />\n你我一齊渡過嘅Moments。  //"},{"pid":"d980c68788ad6661579a2429860069b501b03424","tid":1929624,"uid":198900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T05:15:38.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"5518accf0438c16fbbf8e22236edaeb51438e079","tid":1929624,"uid":121855,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T05:26:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RnrhcAG3gag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRnrhcAG3gag&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8PYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=2df7d4c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RnrhcAG3gag</a><br />\n//問問你這十年<br />\n你拾回了什麼 ?<br />\n<br />\n尊嚴<br />\n信念<br />\n初衷<br />\n回憶<br />\n感受<br />\n快樂<br />\n<br />\n一起拾回屬於自己最真實的<br />\n.<br />\n2019 年<br />\n我學習了很多<br />\n每一天都學習中<br />\n到今天還是在學習中<br />\n明白恐懼本質就是令人害怕<br />\n最後因為害怕令人迷茫<br />\n<br />\n所以只有勇敢<br />\n去接受、承認自己的問題<br />\n正視自己脆弱的內心<br />\n重拾好完整的一個自己<br />\n這也剛好就是這張專輯的概念<br />\n<br />\n這個封面<br />\n在一個無人笑得出的時間內去推出<br />\n好多人都會問：<br />\n仲出碟 ? 你怕唔怕呀 ?<br />\n<br />\n而我只會答你<br />\n我會堅守我歌手的崗位<br />\n就是做好我的音樂<br />\n<br />\n因為我可以做的<br />\n唯一可以做的<br />\n就是這樣<br />\n<br />\n紀錄在我的 2019 年<br />\n.<br />\n小時候認知「正確」的定義 <br />\n由細到大的價值觀<br />\n一直以來看到「人性」的定位 <br />\n好像一下子全都推翻了<br />\n<br />\n最近發生好多好多事<br />\n會很沮喪 會很無奈<br />\n<br />\n越有能力的就應該越懂得解決與處理問題<br />\n掌握權力的就更加要懂得負責與承擔事情<br />\n.<br />\n開首的章節<br />\n在所有崩壞之前 <br />\n前身是綠洲嗎？<br />\n還是一直都只是海市蜃樓<br />\n眼睛被掩蓋住？<br />\n<br />\n這十年應該不只有我相信吧？<br />\n就算所有價值觀倒下<br />\n還有人跟我一起相信心中的畫面<br />\n再建綠洲的優雅？//"},{"pid":"06aa77d3635ff991f299349c9ebdd2f3c09d6cd3","tid":1929624,"uid":121855,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T05:38:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DtOxJYL0ls4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDtOxJYL0ls4&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8PYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=6b6d48e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DtOxJYL0ls4</a><br />\n//慾望與恐懼<br />\n囚禁或釋放<br />\n是人性的執念<br />\n還是心魔作祟<br />\n.<br />\n每日起身都要鼓起勇氣睇新聞，每一日，世界都變得更可笑。<br />\n達賴話，每天起床提醒自己做一個好人，<br />\n比任何信仰都應該更重要。<br />\n.<br />\n2019年究竟去咗邊？<br />\n呢一年所有四字詞語好似都被用壞了<br />\n日落過後<br />\n一切又重新嚟過<br />\n.<br />\n也許祈禱沒有神聽見，但也要祈禱；<br />\n也許沒有佛的因果報應，但也要與人為善；<br />\n也許懷有一顆赤子之心世情也不會有所改變，<br />\n但我們沒有成為罪人，<br />\n我們的世界沒有哈爾這個魔法師，但我們有我們&hearts;️//"},{"pid":"f68f92e37611d99bd8ee0ca2b71ae30986a349fc","tid":1929624,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T05:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36bc56069c982a68d1f5f6c037fc0acde31c2d0","tid":1929624,"uid":137006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ee5aa119631f18a1ff812c4348c8e7fd4465f16","tid":1929624,"uid":18468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T07:05:54.000Z","msg":"share一隊比較underground既<br />\n雖然佢地D歌唔係關政治事<br />\n不過有follow開都知佢地政治取向<br />\n入面所有人都有正職但都好有心機去做歌拍片拍MV<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7olGtMmqVSA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7olGtMmqVSA&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8PYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=5c1f5c2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7olGtMmqVSA</a>"},{"pid":"deeff819f3c883cda73353c8c60dc4c78c0608f1","tid":1929624,"uid":24713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T07:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8166c9cc2f14703e32d15c35642efda02902c4","tid":1929624,"uid":281624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:21:21.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"d27ced837824467db3cef263616fab09f339aa8b","tid":1929624,"uid":121855,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P9U1kwg6toY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DP9U1kwg6toY&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8PYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=1e310a49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P9U1kwg6toY</a><br />\n//〈K〉<br />\n你說不想遠離<br />\n煙霧的滋味<br />\n已看不到距離<br />\n勝利的日期<br />\n朦朧的希冀<br />\n時代的奧秘<br />\n.<br />\n〈P〉<br />\n天地有正氣，雜然賦流形🌑<br />\n而這種廣大充塞的浩然正氣，嚴肅壯烈地永存宇宙之間。<br />\n.<br />\n音樂會大致分為三節，初段迷惘，稍見哀傷。<br />\n中段抗爭意識高漲，不認命的心態強烈。<br />\n後段回歸生活，但也毋忘抗爭。<br />\n整晚的編曲較錄音室版本明顯豐富，音樂的調子不激動，<br />\n但也不是左膠式嘉年華抗爭，而是輕輕淡化負面情緒，<br />\n同時在抗爭之中尋找希望，這就是mla對催淚的滋味的領悟，<br />\n也是送給香港人的療癒之書。//"},{"pid":"826057aad6083eca71d5d4683d39921c40b26da5","tid":1929624,"uid":122110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d27ced837824467db3cef263616fab09f339aa8b","tid":1929624,"uid":121855,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P9U1kwg6toY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DP9U1kwg6toY&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8PYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=1e310a49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P9U1kwg6toY</a><br />\n//〈K〉<br />\n你說不想遠離<br />\n煙霧的滋味<br />\n已看不到距離<br />\n勝利的日期<br />\n朦朧的希冀<br />\n時代的奧秘<br />\n.<br />\n〈P〉<br />\n天地有正氣，雜然賦流形🌑<br />\n而這種廣大充塞的浩然正氣，嚴肅壯烈地永存宇宙之間。<br />\n.<br />\n音樂會大致分為三節，初段迷惘，稍見哀傷。<br />\n中段抗爭意識高漲，不認命的心態強烈。<br />\n後段回歸生活，但也毋忘抗爭。<br />\n整晚的編曲較錄音室版本明顯豐富，音樂的調子不激動，<br />\n但也不是左膠式嘉年華抗爭，而是輕輕淡化負面情緒，<br />\n同時在抗爭之中尋找希望，這就是mla對催淚的滋味的領悟，<br />\n也是送給香港人的療癒之書。//"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T18:57:40.000Z","msg":"犯法為彰顯法制不公允"},{"pid":"8f31878d677ddefe8250ddcf04b4da20331d9e12","tid":1929624,"uid":121855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T05:35:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZHYPoL-sLGk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZHYPoL-sLGk&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8PYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=5f32c848\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZHYPoL-sLGk</a><br />\n//細個聽獅子山，大概係上兩輩引以為傲的獅子山精神。<br />\n千禧年代後漸漸被埋沒甚至唾棄，<br />\n到了現在卻重新給予新的定義。<br />\n而Laser筆不再只是深藍口中的武器，<br />\n爬上獅頭照出的是一道又一道的咆哮。<br />\n.<br />\n今次導演把片尾曲交給我，<br />\n我立刻找了樂隊朋友啊wing共同製作。<br />\n由音符的創作到結他彈奏的聲效，我們都萬分認真對待，<br />\n他更找了自己樂隊的成員啊鼠和子程幫忙錄音 。<br />\n由於我們投身了創作的所有過程，<br />\n所以收到製成品時特別有感覺。<br />\n到了最後混音也去到六七個版本，再找個有感覺的take。<br />\n<br />\n只因大家想作品更加好。<br />\n.<br />\n#為香港人打氣<br />\n.<br />\n這是我的新歌《獅吼記》//"},{"pid":"41cda5fe52a495e24dc77a3583f9e5faa86e4523","tid":1929624,"uid":242980,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8624a1c48fa0d2019dd1c591296d50af03d3eb7c","tid":1929624,"uid":121855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T05:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zvwogqv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzvwogqv.jpg&h=5ad52452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oGZk25x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoGZk25x.jpg&h=9da5e658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZEwvFSf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZEwvFSf.jpg&h=889ad4c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T05:37:34.000Z","msg":"又用啲圖將暴力浪漫化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb5bed7c734f353c463255e61b3203c31cba0eb","tid":1929624,"uid":247139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d90af29d47a00c1499108a99469e326ce0a1b8","tid":1929624,"uid":121855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:01:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K0ZheJfl-gQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DK0ZheJfl-gQ&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8PYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=be31f7ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K0ZheJfl-gQ</a><br />\n//人生中有太多不能控制的事，<br />\n有時會覺得憤怒，有時會覺得憂傷。<br />\n很多時候，以為擱一擱，等一等就會好了，<br />\n到某一天發現自己某部份已經壞了，甚至死了，<br />\n才重新與自己連結。<br />\n<br />\n讀一首詩，唱一首歌，<br />\n用眼淚排解愁煩，在絕望中煉出堅毅與盼望。<br />\n.<br />\n為了守護自己的家<br />\n而走出來的人們。<br />\n<br />\n我們的未來<br />\n都在彼此的手中腳步中。<br />\n<br />\n記住這刻有多憤怒<br />\n某一天用手上的選票<br />\n告訴狼心狗肺的人<br />\n我們想要一個怎樣的未來。<br />\n.<br />\n創作人最珍惜的其中一樣東西是自由表達心中所想，<br />\n相信大家亦是喜歡我們的作品裡的真誠。<br />\n希望大家都能在各自的能力範圍內守護尚有的一切，<br />\n我們才能繼續純粹無慮地創作高歌。<br />\n.<br />\n歌詞就是所有要說的話了。//"},{"pid":"cabd8aa53c9c5414b66274af29431f23eb102b41","tid":1929624,"uid":121855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ee5aa119631f18a1ff812c4348c8e7fd4465f16","tid":1929624,"uid":18468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T07:05:54.000Z","msg":"share一隊比較underground既<br />\n雖然佢地D歌唔係關政治事<br />\n不過有follow開都知佢地政治取向<br />\n入面所有人都有正職但都好有心機去做歌拍片拍MV<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7olGtMmqVSA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7olGtMmqVSA&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8PYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=5c1f5c2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7olGtMmqVSA</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:02:12.000Z","msg":"天水圍驚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c88eb3c4ea6e83ddba492a24b3949d4a0a1ea41","tid":1929624,"uid":5103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">[本土youtube戰線][黃頁］面對偷圖狗，我哋創作愈做愈灰心（認真post)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1932944\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1932944</a><br />\n<br />\n我地已經比人抄到灰哂機<br />\n想請巴打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48cf4f431b9958711544a1efad88979834bedb7","tid":1929624,"uid":121855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c88eb3c4ea6e83ddba492a24b3949d4a0a1ea41","tid":1929624,"uid":5103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">[本土youtube戰線][黃頁］面對偷圖狗，我哋創作愈做愈灰心（認真post)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1932944\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1932944</a><br />\n<br />\n我地已經比人抄到灰哂機<br />\n想請巴打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09b623900152932f7d31d190720f85d8f088e85","tid":1929624,"uid":121855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fjItWzZnX40\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfjItWzZnX40&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8PYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=ec825366\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fjItWzZnX40</a><br />\n//提起「鍾氏兄弟」，不少本地音樂人並不陌生。<br />\n<br />\n2014年雨傘運動那一年，被認為是香港的音樂年，<br />\n他們發表了最後一張碟《極》，<br />\n當中蒐錄了他們創作的好幾首歌，反響不俗，<br />\n包括《時代的顛覆者》、《說不出的未來》2014版本、<br />\n《麻醉式快樂》等。<br />\n<br />\n反送中運動如火如荼，很多年輕人積極投入社運中。<br />\n<br />\n關心香港的Roger也樂見聖歌被唱起，<br />\n或成為音樂創作的另一個契機。<br />\n<br />\nRoger說：「神代表著甚麼呢？祂代表著公義，慈愛，<br />\n即是一些價值，為神發聲就是為公義發聲，為愛發聲，<br />\n就是我們說的行公義、好憐憫。<br />\n憐憫和民主價值是很有關係的，<br />\n因為民主是說一些少數人的聲音，<br />\n我們也會去尊重。這是很重要的價值，<br />\n對於我來說就是要為這些事發聲。」<br />\n<br />\n未來，Roger想做一系列關於香港的項目，<br />\n「因為我覺得香港現在面對的情況，<br />\n是很需要有一些人去保育，去保存一些香港的東西。<br />\n我覺得這些歌曲雖然是屬於某一個年代的產物，<br />\n一個商業的產物，<br />\n但是我覺得我們可以賦予它一些文化的符號，<br />\n而它們可以成為文化的產物。<br />\n我覺得這件事是很值得做，而且隨時都應該做的。」//"},{"pid":"61b4bea3248dba183be3fb5b876c46e01e56947c","tid":1929624,"uid":121855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:09:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jadcbo4NcZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJadcbo4NcZk&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8PYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=0f01fd89\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jadcbo4NcZk</a><br />\n//由一開始去發夢到依家，安安全全接而被搜身，<br />\n抄身分證，社工證；<br />\n然後翻到屋企由仲可以輕鬆打下機寫下歌，到要面對家人話，<br />\n然後驚被人清算.....慢慢好似變得好無感覺咁..... .<br />\n認真我真係好唔鍾意生活係恐懼入面，電話響會驚，<br />\n睇Facebook/IG 會驚，行出街都會驚。 .<br />\n然後望住每日4:00一班Object係度亂up，<br />\n轉個頭睇住義士被捕/虐打/自殺，真係無力感好重！<br />\n到底我可以做咩？ <br />\n我係一個音樂表演者，可能需要低調，<br />\n但我良知唔容許我咁做；我想用自己能力去幫大家！ <br />\n.<br />\n我也希望你可以繼續撐落去<br />\n.<br />\n相信著這個家，身邊的手足<br />\n放下自己嘅無力感覺<br />\n.<br />\n在最艱難的時刻<br />\n我們相信<br />\n只要肯向前邁進<br />\n你便是下一束光//"},{"pid":"e4e2d39019ebaa3d5da2478f948d39ced0ac470d","tid":1929624,"uid":28818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T18:29:05.000Z","msg":"[香港本土書店List]裝飾罷買三中商，中共思想控制香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632803</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8a87dd0e05c677cdb71d3d9c1ae9baf53c359d5b","tid":1929624,"uid":186882,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T19:21:46.000Z","msg":"有d樂隊未必真係黃到金又或者不停喺fb, ig表明自己黃撚到金既立場<br />\n但歌詞中總會睇到一個人既人格<br />\n唱既未必係唱既人既人格，但寫既就一定係果個填詞人既人格<br />\n<br />\n廣東詞界你可以見到倚天劍林夕同屠龍刀Wyman兩位都係閃閃金光<br />\n<br />\n而英文詞壇可以搵Stephen Mok<br />\n由靚詞得黎有禪意既詩式流行曲per se<br />\n到絕望既吶喊Stereo is the answer<br />\n<br />\n新歌City in the ocean完全唱緊中國肺炎下既世界<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s28jmpn3rZU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs28jmpn3rZU&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8PYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=a999e418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s28jmpn3rZU</a><br />\n<br />\n------------<br />\n<br />\nwake up darling<br />\nanother day indulged in luxury<br />\nand then the ocean will say<br />\nwhat have you done<br />\n<br />\nwake up darling<br />\na few more days and we&rsquo;ll be in the sea<br />\nbut all the leaders they say<br />\nno need to be alarmed<br />\n<br />\noh I&rsquo;ve seen the traces<br />\n<br />\nhave you seen why<br />\nthe city&rsquo;s in the ocean?<br />\nat the same time, we&rsquo;re fighting to reward<br />\nourselves as <span style=\"color: red;\">water fill our lungs</span><br />\n<br />\nwake up darling<br />\nanother breath and we&rsquo;ll be in the sea<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">still all the leaders they say<br />\nno need to be alarmed</span><br />\n<br />\noh I&rsquo;ve seen the traces<br />\nheard the screaming<br />\nyet we pay no mind<br />\n<br />\nhave you seen why<br />\nthe city&rsquo;s in the ocean?<br />\nat the same time, we&rsquo;re fighting to reward<br />\nourselves as water, it fills up<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">it&rsquo;ll wash away the glory and the shame</span><br />\nhave you seen why we drown<br />\n<br />\n------------------<br />\n<br />\nIf the world still not wake up by Chinese virus, it'll wash away whole world glory and the shame."},{"pid":"43e56e3d13cf8096a10289644a1005d2c111f3cf","tid":1929624,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T19:24:25.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"2b5f819aad1c66bcbb1f0ed95c9b01887fc35ca0","tid":1929624,"uid":69169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:05:42.000Z","msg":"香港本地仲有好多好好既音樂人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}